676004f760debc96a82","tid":250892,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a5a6e13458493438b431fa1d32735d16267bb63","tid":250892,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵埋海耶克大家爭飽佢</blockquote><br />\n講就天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係經濟一差就叫市場自己調整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你連貨幣都搞唔掂，好心咪搞搞震啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （五常大師：）分開投資同儲蓄做咩勁遮，根本一樣野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRicardo你班古典經濟學家當經濟危機出現嗰陣有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b34ee400270872b739993f1629e322b5b7be3d","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debe6070098d16dcf43ac390231c76c0f12787cf","tid":250892,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係呢啲友搞到金融危機一次又一次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c0308cdaf6db286fc08b50eaec8aaf224048ab","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係呢啲友搞到金融危機一次又一次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> market will balance itself"},{"pid":"e6d71f46c71b641e206d12b1903675e57cbb049e","tid":250892,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fdefe22dc81a05347fa9e9c4a2cb431b731bff","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ed11884ce4d1d905da9b867eca425a6f5b3c20a","tid":250892,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"539de3651cde9c3a0f9211829bf38adade724041","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb7f75359cef62f173175b986ace63c16c819a9","tid":250892,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de678ecd1e8aded64baf43d32aaa9c14c2d9c258","tid":250892,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎完諾貝爾有幾多人記得你？但我就唔同，當年科斯叫我返大陸，係一生中最明智既決定，宜家係十三億人識我，你話邊個決定聰明啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52677679aacd3bb0fca46cf817e1191d72541eaa","tid":250892,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張：Adam Smith都係咁寫書，我就係唔想用艱深數學嚟解釋我理論&mdash;&mdash;《科學說需求》"},{"pid":"b5ffcfba6d1bee991822bdd1d1b00374dcd4fec4","tid":250892,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫幾頁數學公式咪又係空無一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e60c393baac8d0db7e0294e7c6a22a916dd937","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫幾頁數學公式咪又係空無一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇數學支撐既econ=吹水"},{"pid":"b27f0b0b10a5c17ad6ad66c05386e2240acfd4dd","tid":250892,"uid":52593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"問過我未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0bc0632c6ec72a9a271700f4e8f5befbd36eb5","tid":250892,"uid":62012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"啲數計黎計去都錯既 計黎做咩 由市場調整好過啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 Hayek<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1047dbfc4ad5a3f55d42bb491746bdf7f48b5650","tid":250892,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Milton Friedman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫幾頁數學公式咪又係空無一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇數學支撐既econ=吹水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以為有數學就唔係吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54673120ca8758e08d5a84c5af2e551f1cf567fe","tid":250892,"uid":78074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"But this long run is a misleading guide to current affairs. In the long run we are all dead.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad9638bf98c9c5b5c9e21571bfac2fab401f0b2","tid":250892,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"仲有人讀張五常個套咩"},{"pid":"660565ddb3cc5601e6fa8fc83e6a9ec0d6718d17","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我一生中最欣賞就係費老，係我第三次結婚既證婚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫幾頁數學公式咪又係空無一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇數學支撐既econ=吹水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以為有數學就唔係吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咁吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼econometrics, game theory呢d真係可以應用到<br />\n<br />\n但係macro個套9 up理論真係9 up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674ea5a3f98d5f8a93d4c8104b99edd4556d4027","tid":250892,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你條老坑就真係廢老，就黎將行就木都拎唔到諾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n21世紀仲好似作文咁樣寫經濟學書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫幾頁數學公式咪又係空無一物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇數學支撐既econ=吹水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以為有數學就唔係吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇咁吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n起碼econometrics, game theory呢d真係可以應用到<br />\n<br />\n但係macro個套9 up理論真係9 up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGame theory睇唔到，驗證唔到，咪仲9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5616d74e790c774bd8c9af25e0058dc03df30e0","tid":250892,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"你自己個套鬼驗證到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其街上行一圈觀察吓乜嘢research都冇做就當已經做咗驗證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45c1b9932414ed71729ac56ed370e4920f7bdb3","tid":250892,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己個套鬼驗證到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其街上行一圈觀察吓乜嘢research都冇做就當已經做咗驗證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我observation準過啲統計多多聲，我行出條街就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我既專科黎架嘛！"},{"pid":"771f7e3ae95d7756af1dc8ca3eaaf59c81adecb8","tid":250892,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲數計黎計去都錯既 計黎做咩 由市場調整好過啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 Hayek<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n市場調整呢個terms害死香港。十幾年前97左右我就覺得部份香港經濟學家讀死書，好反對佢哋，不過當時全香港好似中毒一樣死吹市場調整。<br />\n<br />\n老實當時香港政府有打算支持IT同創新科技，不過日日俾人屌無形之手干擾市場，最後就找左李擇楷搞數碼港而唔自己出手搞最後變地產項目。<br />\n<br />\n當時屌最勁就係經濟學家雷鼎鳴，日日屌政府，家陣就變689fans，估佔中會唔見3500億。條友為左出名上位害死香港。見一次市場調整terms，就要屌佢老母。"},{"pid":"f274a74954366992f198b3d0a139c5a1bbf71ea9","tid":250892,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cc1e7ea7419ed0747287a0f24c49fc4c762ce62","tid":250892,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你自己個套鬼驗證到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求其街上行一圈觀察吓乜嘢research都冇做就當已經做咗驗證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我observation準過啲統計多多聲，我行出條街就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我既專科黎架嘛！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1398ce71828b793c4fcaaa189dc7e6885a52e61","tid":250892,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]啲數計黎計去都錯既 計黎做咩 由市場調整好過啦<br />\n<br />\n利申 Hayek<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n市場調整呢個terms害死香港。十幾年前97左右我就覺得部份香港經濟學家讀死書，好反對佢哋，不過當時全香港好似中毒一樣死吹市場調整。<br />\n<br />\n老實當時香港政府有打算支持IT同創新科技，不過日日俾人屌無形之手干擾市場，最後就找左李擇楷搞數碼港而唔自己出手搞最後變地產項目。<br />\n<br />\n當時屌最勁就係經濟學家雷鼎鳴，日日屌政府，家陣就變689fans，估佔中會唔見3500億。條友為左出名上位害死香港。見一次市場調整terms，就要屌佢老母。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴呢條欺世盗名既垃圾真係好撚抵屌，個陣佔中條友吹到話做成香港經濟損失幾百億，屌佢老母原來係用恒指升跌計出黎，仲要係用一個星期左右既數據計出黎<br />\n<br />\n得班無知婦孺藍絲先係咁引用佢個「數據」黎打飛機"}]}